<br>
Sotm still has it's place though, defensively.  If you need extra stuns in order to keep a mob from chealing when your lom then switch out w/ this weapon.  ICG's in crypt can be a pain, or the healers in Kael as well.<br>
<br>
I hit for around 115 max w/ no strength buffs on.  So far I have hit 215 with my disc but I'm sure I could go way over that given time.<br>
<br>
Against VS with disc on I was hitting for multiple 100's.  The only way I'd ever change my primary weapon from this now would be to get a vox book.  I'd use FD as a 2ndary tank in a group for more dmg, MDS for tanking w/ sbs as a primary tank.  Or if I lucked up on one of those sweet 32/35 vellium weapons, I'd use that as well.<br>
