Bristlebane <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufenchu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fenchu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/16/01 12:33:33 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Go for Falchion</span><hr size=1> SoM in my opinion other then Darkmetal Falcion is best Pally 1 hander in game...other then the dragon shard...low damage?? are you kidding me, this thing deals out awesome damage...I would take this and shield any day of the week over any 2hander other then epic...the speed of this blade, that stats of a good shield and the Stun proc are amazing, the minute I got one of these at 50 I was soloing anything without a name in Guk...for a Paladin thats great ... Kors went down easy as did Dars..it literally carves through things with a Haste item...and you can Bash....compare this 2 any 2 hander other then epic and you will see that the benefits of this wpn supercede any 2 hander, even though the damage per second may be a bit....yes only a bit higher....Well now I have Darkmetal Falcion and Natures Defender, so no need any more...but SoM is the way to go...<br>
