Eilelin Fenchu<br>
Knight of Tunare <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udfrac.showPublicProfile?language=EN>dfrac</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/17/01 3:52:05 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Well, well, well...</span><hr size=1> It seems that the only people who play Paladins (except me) must be hard-core full-time players in large guilds with well-planned regular large-scale raids. <br>
<br>
I am 56, have earned every PoS item on me the hard way, and am thrilled and delighted with my SotM. To buy it I sacrificed a lot of stuff (I am wearing Jarsath legs and boots now) and I couldn't be happier.<br>
<br>
Now I realise that ANYBODY should just &quot;go out and get&quot; some nifty uber-weapons from the Dragon Necropolis, but please bear in mind, you arrogant asses, that not everyone can.<br>
<br>
